HEADWORD: Lexicology
<hw>Lex`i*col"o*gy</hw> <pr>(l⟦ecr⟧ks`⟦icr⟧*k⟦ocr⟧l"⟦osl⟧*j⟦ycr⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>lexiko`n</grk> lexicon + <ets>-logy</ets>:
cf. F. <ets>lexicologie</ets>.]</ety> <def>The science of the derivation
